      "body": "<p>You can try specifying that it is a relative path by using ` ./` before the file name.</p>\n<p>Check out the answer here <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4210239/how-to-use-relative-path-instead-of-absolute-path\">How to use relative path instead of absolute path?</a>, it might give you a better understanding of how java handles io files.</p>\n"
